# splitscreen

Runs a command twice side by side in a single window.

Usage:

```sh
splitscreen <command>
```

e.g.

```sh
splitscreen glxgears
```


## Installation

```sh
[<PYTHON> -m] pip[3] install [--user] [--upgrade] splitscreen
```


